{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270600/extras/FightHordesOfMonsters_s.png?t=1737754700\" />Drifters &amp; Demons is a top-down shooter where you must defend a settlement against waves of attacking monsters. Humanity hangs on by a thread in a world ravaged by demons and undead. As the leader of the camp, it is your job to keep everyone safe. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">How many days will you survive?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270600/extras/SteamOverdrive.gif?t=1737754700\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270600/extras/BuildAHomelyCamp_s.png?t=1737754700\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Since you're the only one with any real motivation in this god-forsaken camp, you will also have to step up and take on the role of mayor. Build shelters for new survivors and set up shops. Place defenses and upgrade stations. Turrets and traps will play a big part in your survival once the klaxon sounds and the demons start appearing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270600/extras/RescueAndProtectSurvivors_s.png?t=1737754700\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As you expand your camp, survivors will start appearing. Rescue them and build shelters for them and they will pay you back by gathering resources for the camp.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270600/extras/LootUpgradeGainSkills_s.png?t=1737754700\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Aside from looting useful resources, weapons, and equipment during combat, you can also buy and upgrade weapons inside the camp. As the sheriff you can choose new abilities when you have enough experience gems. Metal can be used to buy weapons and defenses, as well as to upgrade them. Salvage can be used to construct new buildings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270600/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737754700","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270600/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1737754700","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270600/bb6f6c77abf5a3e47105a51cd6efeba6052156a0/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737754700","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270600/bb6f6c77abf5a3e47105a51cd6efeba6052156a0/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1737754700","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[5],"notes":"Shooting and killing of demons and zombies, with some cartoon-like blood and gore that can be toggled off. Cartoon-like skeletons and walking corpses."},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270600/extras/FightHordesOfMonsters_s.png?t=1737754700\" />Drifters &amp; Demons is a top-down shooter where you must defend a settlement against waves of attacking monsters. Humanity hangs on by a thread in a world ravaged by demons and undead. As the leader of the camp, it is your job to keep everyone safe. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">How many days will you survive?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270600/extras/SteamOverdrive.gif?t=1737754700\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270600/extras/BuildAHomelyCamp_s.png?t=1737754700\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Since you're the only one with any real motivation in this god-forsaken camp, you will also have to step up and take on the role of mayor. Build shelters for new survivors and set up shops. Place defenses and upgrade stations. Turrets and traps will play a big part in your survival once the klaxon sounds and the demons start appearing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270600/extras/RescueAndProtectSurvivors_s.png?t=1737754700\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As you expand your camp, survivors will start appearing. Rescue them and build shelters for them and they will pay you back by gathering resources for the camp.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270600/extras/LootUpgradeGainSkills_s.png?t=1737754700\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Aside from looting useful resources, weapons, and equipment during combat, you can also buy and upgrade weapons inside the camp. As the sheriff you can choose new abilities when you have enough experience gems. Metal can be used to buy weapons and defenses, as well as to upgrade them. Salvage can be used to construct new buildings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","developers":["Quite Fresh Games"],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"Strategy","id":"2"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270600/header.jpg?t=1737754700","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":[],"mac_requirements":[],"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257066450,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257066450/movie480.mp4?t=1737754692","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257066450/movie_max.mp4?t=1737754692"},"name"